se of this bill is to authorize the Department of Environmental Protection to promulgate a legislative rule relating to hazardous waste management system.This section is new; therefore, strike-throughs and underscoring have been omitted. Bill Status  | Bill Tracking  | Legacy WV Code  | Bulletin Board  | District Maps  | Senate Roster  | House Roster  | Live  | Blog  | Jobs  | Links  | Home This Web site is maintained by the West Virginia Legislature's Office of Reference & Information.  | Terms of Use | Webmaster | © 2025 West Virginia Legislature ** Print On Demand Name: Email: Phone: